          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic06"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">当時は 休憩室でしか喋らない仲やったけれども </p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section--reverse p-about-letter__section07">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic07"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">気になるで収まらず 好きになってしまいました</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bgwhite">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword">それから...</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-stickyContainer">
      <div class = "p-about-bgSticky p-about-bgSticky3"></div>
      <section class = "block3">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section08">
