          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic13"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">そして 俺以上に楽しんでくれたり</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bgwhite">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword p-about-letter__bgword--SP">それ以外にも...</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-stickyContainer">
      <div class = "p-about-bgSticky p-about-bgSticky5"></div>
      <section class = "block5">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section14">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic14"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">古着真剣に選んでくれたり </p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section15">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic15"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">性格について調べてくれたり</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section16">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic16"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">美味しいご飯を作ってくれたり</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bg p-about-letter__background">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__whitePic">
          <img class = "p-about-letter__sticky" src = " <%= image_path %>section/section17.jpeg ">
        </div>
        <div class = "c-speech-bubble">
          <p class = "c-speech-bubble__text c-speech-bubble__text--2">幸せもんですわぁ</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-stickyContainer">
      <div class = "p-about-bgSticky p-about-bgSticky6"></div>
      <section class = "block6">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section--reverse p-about-letter__section18">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic18"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">それに対して俺は</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section--reverse p-about-letter__section19">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic19"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">みなを振り回してばっかやね改めてごめん</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bgwhite--double">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword">みなは</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword p-about-letter__bgword--SP">俺に<br class = "responsive_only">『人としても成長できるきっかけ』を与えてます</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bg p-about-letter__background">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__whitePic">
          <img class = "p-about-letter__sticky" src = " <%= image_path %>section/section20.jpeg ">
        </div>
        <div class = "c-speech-bubble">
          <p class = "c-speech-bubble__text c-speech-bubble__text--3">自分の意見いい！</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "c-speech-bubble">
          <p class = "c-speech-bubble__text c-speech-bubble__text--4">ネガティブやめ</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bg p-about-letter__background">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__whitePic">
          <img class = "p-about-letter__sticky" src = " <%= image_path %>section/section21.jpeg ">
        </div>
        <div class = "c-speech-bubble">
          <p class = "c-speech-bubble__text c-speech-bubble__text--5">優しさを勘違いしてる</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "c-speech-bubble">
          <p class = "c-speech-bubble__text c-speech-bubble__text--6">八方美人は良くない</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-stickyContainer">
      <div class = "p-about-bgSticky p-about-bgSticky7"></div>
      <section class = "block7">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section22">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic22"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">自分で今まで分かってても</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section23">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic23"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">出来へんかった事・間違ってた事</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section24">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic24"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">みなのおかげで</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section25">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic25"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">意識しながら過ごすようになってきました</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bgwhite">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword c-bg-white-img-1 p-about-letter__bgword--SP">（変わるには時間かかるかも知らんけど...）</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-stickyContainer">
      <div class = "p-about-bgSticky p-about-bgSticky8"></div>
      <section class = "block8">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section--reverse p-about-letter__section27">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic27"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">みなには与えて貰ってばっかりです</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section--reverse p-about-letter__section28">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic28"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">でもこれからは</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section--reverse p-about-letter__section29">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic--right p-about-letter__pic29"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--right">お互い『良い影響を与え合える関係性』に成ろうと思ってます</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-stickyContainer">
      <div class = "p-about-bgSticky p-about-bgSticky9"></div>
      <section class = "block9">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section30">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic30"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">まだまだ頼りない俺ですが</p>
        </div>
        <div class = "p-about-letter__section p-about-letter__section31">
          <div class = "p-about-letter__pic p-about-letter__pic31"></div>
          <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--left">これからもよろしくお願いします！</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bgwhite">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword">さいごに...</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class = "p-about-letter__bgwhite">
        <div class = "p-about-letter__bgsection c-bg-white-img-2">
          <p class = "p-about-letter__bgword p-about-letter__bgword--lineHeight">みながホンマに<br class = "responsive_only">『大好き』です</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class = "p-about-letter__myName">
      <p class = "p-about-letter__word p-about-letter__word--center">ばばしょうやより</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="/" class = "c-letterBtn p-about-letterBtn">
    <i class="fas fa-heart c-letterBtn__heart"></i>
    <p class = "c-letterBtn__text p-about-letterBtn__text">手紙を閉じる</p>
  </a>
</main>

<% include src/ejs/template/_footer %>

<script>
  $(function() {
    //windowがスクロールされたら 現れる
    $(window).scroll(function (){
      $('.p-about-letter__word').each(function(){
        var textPosition = $(this).offset().top;
        var scroll = $(window).scrollTop();
        var windowHeight = $(window).height();
        if (scroll > textPosition - windowHeight + 100){
          $(this).addClass('visible2');
        }
      });

      $('.p-about-feature-img__woman').each(function(){
        var textPosition = $(this).offset().top;
        var scroll = $(window).scrollTop();
        var windowHeight = $(window).height();
        if (scroll > textPosition - windowHeight + 100){
          $(this).addClass('visible1');
        }
      });

      $('.p-about-feature-img__man').each(function(){
        var textPosition = $(this).offset().top;
        var scroll = $(window).scrollTop();
        var windowHeight = $(window).height();
        if (scroll > textPosition - windowHeight + 100){
          $(this).addClass('visible1');
        }
      });
    });

    //imgの入れ替わり
    $('.p-about-letter__section').each(function(i, elem){
      var imgPos = $(elem).offset().top;
      $(window).on('load scroll resize', function(){
        var winHeight = $(window).height();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var apper = 500;
        var disapper = 1100;

        // 500px~1100px、コンテンツが見えたら次のif文がtrue
        if (scrollTop >= imgPos  - winHeight + apper && scrollTop <= imgPos  - winHeight + disapper){
          $(elem).addClass('show');
        } else {
          $(elem).removeClass('show');
        }
      });
    });

    $('.p-about-letter__bgwhite').each(function(i, elem){
      var imgPos = $(elem).offset().top;
      $(window).on('load scroll resize', function(){
        var winHeight = $(window).height();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var apper = 400;
        var disapper = 1600;

        if (scrollTop >= imgPos  - winHeight + apper && scrollTop <= imgPos  - winHeight + disapper){
          $(elem).addClass('show');
        } else {
          $(elem).removeClass('show');
        }
      });
    });

    $('.p-about-letter__bgwhite--double').each(function(i, elem){
      var imgPos = $(elem).offset().top;
      $(window).on('load scroll resize', function(){
        var winHeight = $(window).height();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var apper = 400;
        var disapper = 3400;

        if (scrollTop >= imgPos  - winHeight + apper && scrollTop <= imgPos  - winHeight + disapper){
          $(elem).addClass('show');
        } else {
          $(elem).removeClass('show');
        }
      });
    });

    $('.p-about-letter__background').each(function(i, elem){
      var imgPos = $(elem).offset().top;
      $(window).on('load scroll resize', function(){
        var winHeight = $(window).height();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var apper = 400;
        var disapper = 1800;

        if (scrollTop >= imgPos  - winHeight + apper && scrollTop <= imgPos  - winHeight + disapper){
          $(elem).addClass('show');
        } else {
          $(elem).removeClass('show');
        }
      });
    });

    $('.c-speech-bubble').each(function(i, elem){
      var imgPos = $(elem).offset().top;
      $(window).on('load scroll resize', function(){
        var winHeight = $(window).height();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var apper = -500;
        var disapper = -100;

        if (scrollTop >= imgPos  - winHeight + apper && scrollTop <= imgPos  - winHeight + disapper){
          $(elem).addClass('show2');
        } else {
          $(elem).removeClass('show2');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>